<span id="freeTextContainer10996133455210349818">If you didn&apos;t like Verity I wouldn&apos;t read this one, so far the only CH book I&apos;ve liked was , it ends with us</span>
  <span id="freeText10996133455210349818" style="display:none">If you didn't like Verity I wouldn't read this one, so far the only CH book I've liked was , it ends with us</span>
