<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/56732449-the-love-hypothesis"><img alt="The Love Hypothesis (Love Hypothesis, #1)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1611937942l/56732449._SX98_.jpg" />
