<span id="freeTextContainer15088744550895588310">International and #1 New York Times bestselling author of romance, YA, thriller, women&apos;s fiction and paranormal romance. <br/><br/>I don&apos;t like to be confined to one genre. If you put me in a box, I&apos;ll claw my way out. <br/><br/>My social media username is @colleenhoover pretty much everywhere except my email, which is colleenhooverbooks@gmail.com<br/><br/>Founder of <a target='_blank' rel='noopener nofollow' href='http://www.thebookwormbox.com'>www.thebookwormbox.com</a> charity and Book Bonanza.</span>
  <span id="freeText15088744550895588310" style="display:none">International and #1 New York Times bestselling author of romance, YA, thriller, women's fiction and paranormal romance. <br /><br />I don't like to be confined to one genre. If you put me in a box, I'll claw my way out. <br /><br />My social media username is @colleenhoover pretty much everywhere except my email, which is colleenhooverbooks@gmail.com<br /><br />Founder of <a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.thebookwormbox.com">www.thebookwormbox.com</a> charity and Book Bonanza.</span>
